### **9. Metrics and Transparency**

Digital Webducation is committed to transparent, privacy-respecting analytics. From MVP launch, we will track:

* Completion rates of quests and modules
* On-chain credential issuance
* DAO participation metrics
* Community-curated feedback

This data will inform improvements and be publicly accessible to support academic and ecosystem partnerships.

### **10. Call to Action**

Digital Webducation is currently in active development and seeking mission-aligned contributors, communities, and partners. Join us in building the world’s first decentralized, community-owned education platform for Web3 — built on multichain infrastructure, governed by educators and learners.

